# Split Login Pages by Role

The goal is to create separate login pages for each user role (Citizen, Federal, Province, Local) so that accessing a specific URL (e.g., `loginc.html`) directly loads the login form for that role.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> I will be creating new HTML files (`loginc.html`, `logins.html`, `loginp.html`, `loginl.html`) based on [index.html](file:///d:/xampp/htdocs/Hackathon/backend/index.html).
> The new pages will automatically open the authentication modal with the specific role pre-selected.
> I will remove the landing page content from these specific login pages to focus on the login experience.

